overview: On January 15th GCW presents Say You Will live on FITE! The event features the ROH World Championship where Jonathan Gresham faces off 2 Cold Scorpio.  Also in the lineup:  AJ Gray vs PCO  Bandido vs Blake Christian  Allie Katch vs Kylie Rae  Matt Cardona vs Ricky Morton  The Briscoe Brothers vs The Rejects  Jeff Jarrett Returns  Markus Crane Tribute Death match:  Alex Colon vs Jimmy Lloyd vs SHLAK
title: GCW Say You Will
